<p>This tells a client that this is still JSON, but it's some custom vendor format.
If we want to make friends, we should add some extra documentation to <em>our</em> API
that explains how to expect the links and embedded data to come back.</p>
<p>Copy that and go into <code>ProgrammerControllerTest</code> and update our <code>assertEquals()</code> that's
checking for the content type property:</p>
