<p>Finally, copy the test method name and let's make sure everything is looking good:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testPOSTProgrammerWorks</div></code></pre>
<p>All green!</p>
<p>I really love this HATEOAS library because it's so easy to add links to your API.
But it doesn't mean that you have to live with HAL JSON. You can use a different
official format or invent your own.</p>

    
